Automated Signup Test – Selenium
Project Overview
This project contains an automated end-to-end Signup test for a web application 
using Selenium WebDriver, TestNG, and Extent Reports.

Tech Stack 
Language & Frameworks
-Java (JDK 11 or above)
-Selenium WebDriver
-TestNG (test framework)
-Extent Reports (v5) – for HTML reporting
-MailSlurp API – for OTP email handling
-Jsoup – for parsing OTP from email HTML

Tools
-Maven – dependency management
-IntelliJ IDEA (recommended IDE)
-Google Chrome browser

Prerequisites
Before running the test, ensure:
1. Java JDK 11+ is installed
2. Maven is installed and configured
3. Google Chrome browser is installed
4. ChromeDriver is available in PATH
5. Internet connection is available (for MailSlurp & application access)

Environment Variables
MailSlurp API Key
For security reasons, the MailSlurp API key is not hardcoded.
Set the API key as an environment variable:
